ノンデリシャス なんべんだってオカワリ
Non-delicious, seconds as many times as you want

740
00:51:51,080 --> 00:51:51,880
おえっ
Ugh

741
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:55,280
お皿積む 積み上げ 3, 4, 5
Piling up the plates, three, four, five

742
00:51:55,380 --> 00:51:59,280
バベルみたいに 3, 4, 5
Like the Tower of Babel, three, four, five

743
00:51:59,480 --> 00:52:03,080
喉の奥につっかえて窒息しかけても
Even if it gets stuck in the throat and almost chokes me

744
00:52:03,180 --> 00:52:08,080
大人は飲み込むらしい すっごいね
Apparently adults just swallow it, how amazing

745
00:52:10,080 --> 00:52:14,080
見栄と意地のソテー 義理人情サンドイッチ
Sauteed vanity and stubbornness, duty and humanity sandwich

746
00:52:14,180 --> 00:52:17,580
情熱の冷めたスープ
A soup where passion has cooled down

747
00:52:17,680 --> 00:52:21,080
そんなもの頼んでないから
Since I didn't order anything like that

748
